---
title: Southwestern Pork Meatballs with Roast Potatoes & BBQ Sauce
description: We got inspired by our American friends and their use of smokey, sweet and spiced flavours in Southwestern meals. That’s why these meatballs are studded with corn and served with herbed wedges for a new take on dinner that will quickly become an instant classic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c074adfc445fa3eaa472742-47ae49f4.jpg
